Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.74,HnF,,0,0,0,,Febrero
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:41.98,HnF,,0,0,0,,Qué decepción.{How sloppy.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:46.68,HnF,,0,0,0,,La pelea del verano pasado fue más emocionante.{When we fought last summer you had more backbone, didn't you?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.16,0:00:54.54,HnF,,0,0,0,,Me he estado conteniendo mucho más que entonces.{ I've pretty much been holding back this time, entirely.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.54,0:00:56.99,HnF,,0,0,0,,Sí. Lo he notado.{I appreciate that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:59.95,HnF,,0,0,0,,De todas formas, ¿qué pretendes{Anyway, what are you after,}\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:02.83,HnF,,0,0,0,,retándome de repente{challenging me to a fight all of a sudden}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:03.96,HnF,,0,0,0,,Finales de Febrero
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:06.46,HnF,,0,0,0,,Muchas cosas me están angustiando últimamente,{A lot of things have hit a stopping point for me,}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:10.25,HnF,,0,0,0,,así que pensé que tal vez podría prepararme con tu ayuda.{so I thought maybe I'd see if I could get some training from you, Kagenui-san.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:15.84,HnF,,0,0,0,,Estaba pensando que estaría bien que la próxima vez que me encuentre en una situación peligrosa{I was thinking it'd be nice if, the next time I'm met with a difficult situation,}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:20.89,HnF,,0,0,0,,pueda manejarla por mi cuenta, como lo harías tú,\N sin depender de mis poderes de vampiro.{I could deal with it as deftly as you, and without relying on my vampirism.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.94,0:01:25.44,HnF,,0,0,0,,Ya veo, así que se trata de eso.{Oh, I see. That's what this is about.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.44,0:01:28.06,HnF,,0,0,0,,Pero probablemente deberías de tirar la toalla.{But you should probably give up on that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:33.36,HnF,,0,0,0,,\NSi fueses a intentar aprender mi técnica mientras practicamos en una batalla{If you were to try and learn my technique from me like this in live battle practice,}\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:36.53,HnF,,0,0,0,,probablemente morirías antes de poder aprenderla.{you would die before you learned it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:44.45,HnF,,0,0,0,,¿Por qué crees que he enviado a Yotsugi para infiltrarse en tu casa?{Just why exactly do you think I've sent Yotsugi to invade your house?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:50.17,HnF,,0,0,0,,De esa forma, podrías evitar cualquier problema relacionado con excentricidades por un tiempo.{For a little while at least, I've made it so that you should be able to go without being bothered by oddity affairs.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:59.53,HnF,,0,0,0,,Es exactamente eso, viviendo el día a día protegido por dos mujeres me hace sentir patético.{It's just that, living my everyday life being protected by two little girls kinda makes me feel sorry for myself.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.03,0:02:04.93,HnF,,0,0,0,,Pero también es por eso que puedes vivir \Nsin preocuparte por cada movimiento, ¿no es así?{And that is exactly why you can't carelessly make a move, now isn't it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:06.52,HnF,,0,0,0,,Al igual que {\i1}ellos.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:14.32,HnF,,0,0,0,,Como sea, no deberías hacer cosas peligrosas como intentar aprender algo de mí.{In any case, you shouldn't be doing extreme things like trying to learn anything from me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:20.03,HnF,,0,0,0,,Kagenui, ¿cómo te involucraste con las excentricidades?{Why did you get involved with oddities and ghost stories, Kagenui-san?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:25.37,HnF,,0,0,0,,Probablemente comenzó en parvulario, cuando pegué a un niño irritante.{It probably started back in kindergarten, when I punched some irritating kid.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:31.50,HnF,,0,0,0,,Ahora que lo pienso, ese niño podría haber estado poseído por alguna que otra cosa.{Thinking about it now, that brat might have been possessed by some awful thing or another, too.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:36.05,HnF,,0,0,0,,Pero eso fue mucho antes de que me \Nespecializase en excentricidades inmortales.{Though that was from back before I specialized in immortal oddities.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:40.84,HnF,,0,0,0,,Así que la razón por la que te especializaste en las excentricidades inmortales{So, the reason you specialize in taking on immortal oddities right now,}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:44.01,HnF,,0,0,0,,si no recuerdo mal es porque\N 'no se puede complicar más de lo que está'.{\Nwas because it 'wasn't possible to overdo it,' if I recall.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:49.10,HnF,,0,0,0,,¿Eso quiere decir que las situaciones siempre acaban por torcerse? {\NTurning that around, that would mean that you've overdone it quite a lot of times before, wouldn't it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.32,HnF,,0,0,0,,¿Son gajes del oficio?{\NIs your profession perhaps based on this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:54.03,HnF,,0,0,0,,Supongo que puedes llamarlo así.{I suppose you could say that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:57.28,HnF,,0,0,0,,Estás preguntando muchas cosas.{You sure have a lot of questions.\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:00.78,HnF,,0,0,0,,¿Estás planeando que me una yo también?{What, do you want me to join, too?\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:03.66,HnF,,0,0,0,,Al rumoreado harén de Araragi.{To the fabled 'Araragi harem' or whatever you call it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.08,HnF_Pensa,,0,0,0,,¿¡Cómo se ha enterado!?{Why does she know about that?!\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:08.66,HnF_Pensa,,0,0,0,,Quiero decir, no existe ninguna organización con ese nombre.{Er, no. No such scandalous organization actually exists.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:12.92,HnF,,0,0,0,,Estaría bien que tuviese suficiente poder para poder cortejarte{It'd be nice if I could become enough of a big-shot to woo you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:17.17,HnF,,0,0,0,,pero ahora mismo me preocupa más permanecer siendo humano que eso.{\NThough right now I'm more worried about staying human than getting big.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:21.18,HnF,,0,0,0,,No te preocupes, si pierdes tu humanidad me encargaré personalmente de acabar contigo.{Don't worry, if you do lose your humanity, I'll be here to beat you to death.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.31,HnF,,0,0,0,,Oye, Kagenui.{Hey, Kagenui-san?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:28.44,HnF,,0,0,0,,¿Qué pasa?{What is it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:32.44,HnF,,0,0,0,,¿Qué relación tienes con Ononoki?{How are you and Ononoki-chan related to each other?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:35.02,HnF,,0,0,0,,¿Mi relación con Yotsugi?{ My relationship with Yotsugi?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:39.70,HnF,,0,0,0,,Como ya sabes, yo soy la exorcista, y ella mi herramienta ceremonial.{ As you already know, I'm the exorcist and she is my shikigami.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:44.86,HnF,,0,0,0,,Pero Ononoki se refiere a ti como {\i1}hermana{\i0}, {Yeah, but, well, Ononoki-chan refer to you as 'big sister,' now doesn't she?}¿no es así?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.12,HnF,,0,0,0,,Así es.{She does.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:50.71,HnF,,0,0,0,,Por eso me preguntaba si las dos teníais ese tipo de relación fraternal. {So, I was wondering if you two had kind of a sisterly relationship or something.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.67,HnF,,0,0,0,,Puesto de esa forma:{If you're gonna say that, it's like this:}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:56.29,HnF,,0,0,0,,Ella se refiere a ti como hermano, ¿no?{\NShe says big brother when referring to you, too, doesn't she?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:59.96,HnF,,0,0,0,,En la mayoría de los casos se refiere a la gente como hermano.{\NShe says big brother and big sister when referring to most people.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:00.63,HnF,,0,0,0,,Hermano Oshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:01.59,HnF,,0,0,0,,Hermano Kaiki.{Big brother Kaiki}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.34,HnF,,0,0,0,,Sí, pero...{Yes... but,\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:06.97,HnF,,0,0,0,,Pero a ti se refiere como 'mi hermana'.{she calls you just 'big sister.'}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:15.52,HnF,,0,0,0,,Eres un tipo muy observador.{ Well, aren't you the perceptive fellow.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:16.85,HnF,,0,0,0,,¿O tal vez tienes una buena intuición?{Or maybe you have good intuition?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:20.40,HnF,,0,0,0,,Aunque bueno, no es algo que me interese esconder,{Well, it's not really something worth hiding,}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.36,HnF,,0,0,0,,y no me importaría decírtelo,{and it wouldn't really matter if I told you,}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:27.72,HnF,,0,0,0,,pero preguntármelo de esa forma tan presuntuosa me hace pensar en qué hacer.{but being asked so formally somehow makes me not want to tell you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:30.22,HnF,,0,0,0,,¿Entonces no me lo dirás?{Then, you won't tell me?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:32.00,HnF,,0,0,0,,No, no he dicho eso.{No, I'm not saying I won't.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.08,HnF,,0,0,0,,Tampoco voy a pedirte dinero o favores{I also won't ask for anything like a payment of favors or money}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:34.25,HnF,,0,0,0,,así que no te preocupes por eso.{so don't worry yourself about that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:35.75,HnF,,0,0,0,,Eso es,{Okay then,}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.42,HnF,,0,0,0,,¿qué te parece continuar nuestra pelea de antes?{how about a continuation of our battle?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:40.55,HnF,,0,0,0,,Un sólo golpe.{Just one shot.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:45.22,HnF,,0,0,0,,Si logras acertar un solo golpe durante la pelea{\NIf you manage to land just one shot while matched against me,}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:47.18,HnF,,0,0,0,,entonces te lo diré.{\NI'll tell you then.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.93,HnF,,0,0,0,,La verdadera identidad de Yotsugi.{\NYotsugi's true identity.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:52.31,HnF,,0,0,0,,{\pos(466,342)}Encantamiento mágico{Magical incantation}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.94,HnF,,0,0,0,,Y es por eso, Karen, es tu turno.{And so that's why, Karen-chan, it's your turn.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:57.65,HnF,,0,0,0,,¿Qué quieres decir exactamente con 'es por eso'?{Um, what exactly do you mean by 'that's why'?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.23,HnF,,0,0,0,,No-puedo-contarte-los-detalles,{I-can't-talk-about-the-details,}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.02,HnF,,0,0,0,,pero-hay-alguien-que-es-muy-poderoso,{but-there's-this-person-who's-strong-as-an-ox.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:01.40,HnF,,0,0,0,,tanto-que-no-tengo-nada-que-hacer{so-strong-that-I'm-utterly-powerless-against-them,}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.69,HnF,,0,0,0,,pero-quiero-darle-un-golpe.{but-I-want-to-land-a-punch-on-them.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.90,HnF,,0,0,0,,¿Hay algo que pueda hacer?{Is there anything I can do?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:04.25,HnF,,0,0,0,,{\pos(237.333,315.668)}¿Quién {who}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:04.25,HnF,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722.667,306.334)}se cree{exactly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:05.11,HnF,,0,0,0,,{\pos(239,329)}mi \Nhermano{does}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:05.11,HnF,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726,316)}que{my \Nbrother}
